00:40:53.420 --> 00:40:54.170
ANTOINE BELLO: OK.

00:40:54.170 --> 00:40:55.980
I get the question.

00:40:55.980 --> 00:40:57.410
I'm not really sure about that.

00:40:57.410 --> 00:41:00.710
Probably the best
story about democracy

00:41:00.710 --> 00:41:03.170
is the American story.

00:41:03.170 --> 00:41:05.090
They did a pretty good job.

00:41:05.090 --> 00:41:06.800
They did a very, very good job.

00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:10.460
The house up on the hill
and the promised land

00:41:10.460 --> 00:41:12.800
and the Constitution,
the Founding Fathers,

00:41:12.800 --> 00:41:18.080
all that wisdom pouring into
the country; a text that

00:41:18.080 --> 00:41:25.730
has withstood the test of
time; the justices that

00:41:25.730 --> 00:41:29.780
can tell the law once
in a while when need be;

00:41:29.780 --> 00:41:33.600
the president, the
checks and balances--

00:41:33.600 --> 00:41:35.240
it's a very, very good story.

00:41:35.240 --> 00:41:39.860
I live there and I base
in that story every day,

00:41:39.860 --> 00:41:44.420
and I have to say, as a
storyteller, everyday I think,

00:41:44.420 --> 00:41:45.687
they're pretty good.

00:41:45.687 --> 00:41:46.520
They're pretty good.

00:41:49.490 --> 00:41:57.170
Yes, the fascist
regimes, for instance,

00:41:57.170 --> 00:42:00.020
have different stories and
can have compelling stories

00:42:00.020 --> 00:42:03.680
if you are in the right camp.

00:42:03.680 --> 00:42:07.970
If you're not one of
the Jews or homosexuals,

00:42:07.970 --> 00:42:10.130
I guess you might
like that story.

00:42:10.130 --> 00:42:12.690
Some people don't.

00:42:12.690 --> 00:42:16.470
But those stories, honestly,
I'm not sure they're that good.

00:42:16.470 --> 00:42:20.010
I mean, when you think about
the national socialism,

00:42:20.010 --> 00:42:23.930
it lasted for only
10 years, 12 years.

00:42:23.930 --> 00:42:26.990
Communism is almost--
well, I won't

00:42:26.990 --> 00:42:32.540
say forgotten, but
except for Venezuela

00:42:32.540 --> 00:42:37.370
and I won't say
China, but it has

00:42:37.370 --> 00:42:42.060
disappeared from almost
everywhere in the world.

00:42:42.060 --> 00:42:44.330
It's what I was trying to say.

00:42:44.330 --> 00:42:48.350
Religions usually last much
longer than political ideals.

00:42:48.350 --> 00:42:55.130
Political ideas pass much
more quickly than we think.

00:42:58.570 --> 00:42:59.070
Yes.

